{"tid":1070095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運房局確認港鐵公司會被罰款","createTime":"2019-03-20T11:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T12:42:22.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"08bdbbd656b15a1a3e31f63150494a67ae5f51ce","tid":1070095,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"港鐵因測試新信號系統導致兩列車相撞，經兩日搶修後，荃灣線服務今早回復正常。運房局發言人表示，根據票價調整機制內「服務表現安排」，港鐵發生31分鐘或以上因機件故障或人為因素導致的服務延誤事故，即會被罰款，款項將會放入票價優惠帳戶，透過「車費優惠」回饋乘客。受今次事故影響，荃灣綫來往中環站與金鐘站的列車服務暫停了兩天（3月18日及19日），港鐵公司會被罰款。 <br />\n現階段，政府部門及港鐵公司最重要的工作是捉緊時間就事故進行詳細調查。同時，政府亦會與港鐵嚴肅跟進罰款的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/960847-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%92%9E%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%91%E9%81%8B%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%80%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%9C%83%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F960847-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%2592%259E%25E8%25BB%258A%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2581%258B%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV9nRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=63c288be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F960847-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%2592%259E%25E8%25BB%258A%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2581%258B%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE&h=92273bd6\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/960847-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%92%9E%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%91%E9%81%8B%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%80%E7%A2